•	Streamlit: For building the interactive web application and visualizing the data.
•	React: For creating the landing page and front-end interface.
•	Pandas: For data manipulation and analysis.
•	Plotly: For creating interactive visualizations (Bar, Pie, Bubble, and Donut charts).
•	Matplotlib: For generating static visualizations.
•	NLTK: For text analysis and report generation.
•	AutoViz: For performing automated Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA).
•	Sumy: For text summarization and generating concise reports.
•	MongoDB: For storing employee data (if applicable).
•	Python: Core language for backend logic and data processing.
•	Excel/CSV Files: Data input format for the application.
